summary: 2048 x 2048 resolution of the Skeever. New custom textures used.
descriptionHtml:
[color=Lightskyblue][b]-Reviews-[/b][/color]
jezamarie Says:
[color=gold][size=5]"Ewww! Now they're even grosser! Good job though, they look good."[/size][/color]

Els236 says:
[color=gold][size=5]"These look so much better than the vanilla skeevers!"[/size][/color]

If you like my work please remember to endorse!

[color=silver][size=4]Yet another forgotten creature that looks awful on low, medium, high and ultra high settings. This mod fixes that. Using my own textures I have given the Skeever a more detailed, less pixelated look. This mod re-textures both black and white Skeevers.[/size][/color]

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21962]Wolverine2710's Automatic Variants Port for my Better Skeever[/url]
author: yourenotsupposedtobeinhere
